03:32:10,365 --> 03:32:14,368
[SPEAKER_44]: So it would be a motion requesting that the mayor

2773
03:32:16,681 --> 03:32:42,093
[SPEAKER_44]: provide the council with a full description of the standards or procedures the mayor uses in determining what banners or signs will be allowed to be placed on city hall.

