2794
03:34:22,589 --> 03:34:24,871
[SPEAKER_29]: The First Amendment is designed to protect

2795
03:34:26,474 --> 03:34:35,196
[SPEAKER_29]: citizens of the United States, and it's incorporated to the Commonwealth of Massachusetts through the 14th Amendment, from the government interfering with the private right to communicate.

2796
