2802
03:35:02,288 --> 03:35:05,370
[SPEAKER_29]: The city has a complete right to put messages up on city property.

2803
03:35:05,850 --> 03:35:17,277
[SPEAKER_29]: It doesn't have the right to infringe on private property and, well, it doesn't have the right to infringe on the residents' use of their free speech or freedom of expression.

2804
03:35:20,399 --> 03:35:21,720
[SPEAKER_37]: Point of information, Mr. President?

2805
