2830
03:38:13,883 --> 03:38:20,109
[SPEAKER_44]: But unless he already approached the mayor, and the mayor denied him of the sign, which I'm not sure.

2831
03:38:20,649 --> 03:38:28,716
[SPEAKER_44]: But clearly, the city administration has control, as well as the building commissioner of the buildings, and it's not the city council.

2832
03:38:29,036 --> 03:38:34,061
[SPEAKER_44]: But I'm willing, Mr. President, to find out what the rules and regulations are and move that forward.

2833
03:38:36,183 --> 03:38:37,144
[SPEAKER_37]: Thank you, Councilor Marks.

