2846
03:39:19,738 --> 03:39:21,859
[SPEAKER_43]: In my opinion, um, black lives matter.

2847
03:39:22,199 --> 03:39:23,140
[SPEAKER_43]: I have no problem saying it.

2848
03:39:23,780 --> 03:39:26,361
[SPEAKER_43]: Um, but Mr. President, you know, we're a government organization.

2849
03:39:26,381 --> 03:39:28,762
[SPEAKER_43]: We're a government entity and we have to operate like one.

2850
03:39:29,521 --> 03:39:35,104
[SPEAKER_43]: I personally don't wanna sit here every week and debate the merits of what sign they're gonna hang up next on City Hall.

2851
03:39:35,384 --> 03:39:39,066
