3309
04:14:12,020 --> 04:14:17,283
[SPEAKER_18]: And I wish that you could all understand this and feel it the way I do.

3310
04:14:20,285 --> 04:14:20,665
[SPEAKER_18]: Thank you.

3311
04:14:20,685 --> 04:14:27,089
[SPEAKER_37]: Okay, let's see.

3312
04:14:27,989 --> 04:14:29,390
[SPEAKER_37]: Okay, any other questions or comments?

3313
04:14:33,443 --> 04:14:37,544
[SPEAKER_49]: Mr. President.

3314
04:14:37,584 --> 04:14:39,825
[SPEAKER_49]: Let me, let me, uh, thank you, Mr. President.

3315
