[SPEAKER_49]: This is difficult doing, uh, our meetings and zoom by phone.

3316
04:14:45,086 --> 04:14:45,786
[SPEAKER_49]: It's terrible.

3317
04:14:45,846 --> 04:14:50,768
[SPEAKER_49]: So you don't want to at times that someone's speaking, you have a difficult time to try to jump in.

3318
04:14:51,328 --> 04:15:02,271
[SPEAKER_49]: So I, I appreciate, and I understand the black lives matter, uh, statement and it means so much because as I talked about

3319
04:15:03,047 --> 04:15:25,195
[SPEAKER_49]: uh... and many meetings the the discussion that i've had with my my friends uh... of color and talking to my uh... uh... black colleagues in and and former players in players in talking about you know the the actual black lives matter uh... banner it it it's funny how

3320
04:15:26,067 --> 04:15:47,566
[SPEAKER_49]: You can hear, I forgot, I apologize, the last speaker who just spoke, you can hear the intense hurt in her voice and that breaks my heart because as I talk to my friends that are black and we debate these concerns or lack of concerns,

3321
04:15:53,399 --> 04:15:59,282
