3331
04:17:02,959 --> 04:17:07,622
[SPEAKER_49]: Because we do have racial issues in our country.

3332
04:17:09,242 --> 04:17:10,483
[SPEAKER_49]: But I think it's important that

3333
04:17:11,201 --> 04:17:19,547
