3340
04:17:45,973 --> 04:17:48,154
[SPEAKER_49]: And I have to live with the decisions I make, right or wrong.

3341
04:17:49,154 --> 04:18:03,097
[SPEAKER_49]: But it's comical that in a past meeting that I had hundreds of phone calls from my former players and my friends of color that said, George, why didn't you respond to that woman that called you a racist?

3342
04:18:04,443 --> 04:18:10,986
