3347
04:18:46,755 --> 04:18:50,236
[SPEAKER_49]: And the point that I'm trying to make is very simple.

3348
04:18:50,517 --> 04:18:51,617
[SPEAKER_49]: Black lives do matter.

3349
04:18:52,817 --> 04:18:56,999
[SPEAKER_49]: And as I stand with my friends of color, they know George Scott probably knows that.

3350
04:18:58,007 --> 04:19:03,832
