3353
04:19:12,259 --> 04:19:14,381
[SPEAKER_49]: There's a reason why everybody moved to Medford.

3354
04:19:14,741 --> 04:19:16,163
[SPEAKER_49]: Medford is a great community.

3355
04:19:16,763 --> 04:19:18,044
[SPEAKER_49]: We love Medford, all of us.

3356
04:19:19,405 --> 04:19:19,786
[SPEAKER_49]: All of us.

3357
04:19:21,932 --> 04:19:31,274
[SPEAKER_49]: Whether you're fighting for your own social causes, or whether you've lived here for 35 years, it doesn't matter.

3358
04:19:31,334 --> 04:19:34,914
[SPEAKER_49]: We have to find a common ground to bring Metro back together.

3359
04:19:34,934 --> 04:19:44,256
[SPEAKER_49]: Because I've heard so many people, the disappointment in our elderly, in our people that have just moved to the city, to say that, why are we so divided?

3360
04:19:44,356 --> 04:19:45,496
[SPEAKER_49]: We need to come together.

3361
04:19:47,357 --> 04:19:48,577
[SPEAKER_49]: So we need it from the leadership.

3362
04:19:49,454 --> 04:19:52,995
[SPEAKER_49]: Now the male will follow this process, and then we will follow this process.

3363
04:19:53,295 --> 04:20:05,539
[SPEAKER_49]: And if the Black Lives Matter sign hangs in Medford, and that now sends a message to everybody in our community that we stand together with Black lives, that's the process we went through.

3364
04:20:05,559 --> 04:20:07,019
[SPEAKER_49]: And we shall be proud of that.

3365
04:20:09,300 --> 04:20:17,482
[SPEAKER_49]: But at the same time, to say, everybody say that this isn't a political statement, this is what's dividing us.

3366
04:20:18,160 --> 04:20:27,625
[SPEAKER_49]: Because A, it is, and then B, the people that are looking at it the other side, they're not looking at it as how to help our black brothers and sisters.

3367
04:20:28,765 --> 04:20:36,309
[SPEAKER_49]: It's being looked at to say, well, let's look at that political group that's breaking our community down.

3368
04:20:37,970 --> 04:20:40,772
[SPEAKER_49]: And in a sense, yes, it does make some people look racist.

3369
04:20:42,673 --> 04:20:43,933
[SPEAKER_49]: And I don't think that's the intent.

3370
