[SPEAKER_49]: Unfortunately, I'm not naive.

3371
04:20:47,865 --> 04:20:48,965
[SPEAKER_49]: Racism does exist.

3372
04:20:50,346 --> 04:21:12,331
[SPEAKER_49]: But I tell you, when I talk to my friends of color, and I talk to them, and how sad it is when they tell me that their kids are afraid to go to school because of one reason or another, or our white kids are afraid to go to school because they're put on a list that they've used a racial slur.

3373
04:21:15,470 --> 04:21:16,631
[SPEAKER_49]: It's dividing this community.

3374
04:21:16,671 --> 04:21:19,532
[SPEAKER_49]: We need to find something that's going to bring this together.

3375
04:21:19,572 --> 04:21:36,518
[SPEAKER_49]: So if we can follow through with Councilman Moxley's suggestions, and we make sure we dot our I's and cross our T's, and that's the resolution that we now hang the Black Lives Matter at Methodist City Hall, and that's the way we go.

3376
04:21:36,818 --> 04:21:43,540
[SPEAKER_49]: We need to find a way to stand together and heal and stop dividing.

3377
04:21:45,876 --> 04:22:05,580
[SPEAKER_49]: So believe me, I work in the community that first put that banner out, and I'm telling you, whatever you want to think, whether you're white or black, I heard from every single color that came to talk to me that looked at that as a platform instead of what's really intended for.

3378
04:22:05,600 --> 04:22:09,640
[SPEAKER_49]: And it divided people in that community, both black and white.

3379
04:22:10,341 --> 04:22:12,801
[SPEAKER_49]: And black people were for it, and black people were against it.

3380
04:22:15,171 --> 04:22:19,973
[SPEAKER_49]: So this is bigger, this is made up bigger than it really is.

3381
04:22:20,893 --> 04:22:22,774
[SPEAKER_49]: And it has, and it shouldn't.

3382
04:22:24,955 --> 04:22:30,637
[SPEAKER_49]: So all I beg to everybody in our community is let this take its course.

3383
04:22:32,698 --> 04:22:35,039
[SPEAKER_49]: And let's find a way to all come together and heal.

3384
04:22:36,120 --> 04:22:38,481
[SPEAKER_49]: Because when we voted on making

3385
04:22:39,580 --> 04:22:43,902
[SPEAKER_49]: making, um, uh, announcing, uh, racism, uh, public health emergency.

3386
04:22:43,942 --> 04:22:44,863
[SPEAKER_49]: I voted no on that.

3387
04:22:45,183 --> 04:22:50,046
[SPEAKER_49]: And I got feedback because I'm racist, but here we are here.

3388
04:22:50,086 --> 04:22:51,466
[SPEAKER_49]: We are months later.

3389
04:22:54,388 --> 04:22:59,050
[SPEAKER_49]: And like I said, nothing has been done as a community.

3390
04:22:59,091 --> 04:23:01,692
[SPEAKER_49]: We've done nothing to bring people together.

3391
04:23:02,947 --> 04:23:06,388
[SPEAKER_49]: I've asked for our black leaders in our community.

3392
04:23:06,668 --> 04:23:13,950
