3394
04:23:25,093 --> 04:23:26,893
[SPEAKER_49]: So we all understand how we need to heal.

3395
04:23:28,246 --> 04:23:35,651
[SPEAKER_49]: And I know one council said, shame on you want, you want, now you want people to people of color to teach us what's wrong.

3396
04:23:36,952 --> 04:23:38,613
[SPEAKER_49]: Yes, we need to.

3397
04:23:40,734 --> 04:23:42,875
[SPEAKER_49]: Because that color of skin does not match theirs.

3398
04:23:43,296 --> 04:23:45,177
[SPEAKER_49]: And we've never lived what they're living through.

3399
