[SPEAKER_49]: Overly winded Mr. President, but I thought I knew that had to be said.

3401
04:23:53,622 --> 04:23:54,162
[SPEAKER_49]: So thank you.

3402
04:23:54,603 --> 04:23:54,903
[SPEAKER_31]: Thank you.

3403
04:23:54,923 --> 04:23:55,863
[SPEAKER_31]: Councilor Scott Kelly.

3404
04:23:55,884 --> 04:23:56,484
[SPEAKER_31]: Councilor Laurel.

3405
04:23:57,773 --> 04:23:58,633
[SPEAKER_31]: Thank you, Mr. President.

3406
04:23:58,693 --> 04:24:02,355
