[SPEAKER_53]: I just wanted to change to something I said previously.

3462
04:27:36,980 --> 04:27:40,462
[SPEAKER_53]: I was suggesting that both of these resolutions or both of these things were voted upon.

3463
04:27:40,922 --> 04:27:45,345
[SPEAKER_53]: But now that it's completely clear, it's absolutely clear that this is just a recommendation to the mayor's office.

3464
04:27:45,665 --> 04:27:49,508
[SPEAKER_53]: This is in no shape or form a violation of a separation of powers.

3465
04:27:50,248 --> 04:27:55,151
[SPEAKER_53]: There's no reason that I could possibly see why this particular council needs any kind of clarification.

3466
04:27:55,171 --> 04:27:57,613
